{"tid":1016847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(熱烈祝賀) 日本建國紀念日   安倍誓言開創更美好未來","createTime":"2019-02-11T04:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T10:34:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0337564a1dd8261f379301557eef3a564b3a12d1","tid":1016847,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://simg314.magcasa.com/content_images/2016/01/02/210424/1451717113_6866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsimg314.magcasa.com%2Fcontent_images%2F2016%2F01%2F02%2F210424%2F1451717113_6866.jpg&h=bf5d47a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天是日本的「建國紀念之日」，首相安倍晉三發表談話指出，放眼平成的下一個時代，也將繼續為了子孫努力下去，開創一個更加美好的未來。<br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）報導，安倍今天對平成年代最後一次的「建國紀念之日」發表談話。他從2014年以來每年都會在這一天發表談話。<br />\n<br />\n安倍說，在漫長的歷史中，日本多次面對重大困難及嚴酷考驗，但每次都在前人抱持勇氣與希望的情況下恢復，並建設成今日和平且富足的國家。<br />\n<br />\n他說，在守護傳統的同時也不懼怕變化，即時面對困難的課題也會勇敢克服；他們過去一直以來持續做這樣的努力，放眼平成的下一個時代，也將繼續為了子孫努力下去，開創一個更加美好的未來，「我重新下定這個決心」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5-%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E8%AA%93%E8%A8%80%E9%96%8B%E5%89%B5%E6%9B%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86-030810047.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2580%258D%25E8%25AA%2593%25E8%25A8%2580%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%259B%25B4%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586-030810047.html&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo5%2FdVh5kQGr0UM1CkPSjmotI%3D&h=e3033bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5-%E5%AE%89%E5%80%8D%E8%AA%93%E8%A8%80%E9%96%8B%E5%89%B5%E6%9B%B4%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86-030810047.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://simg314.magcasa.com/content_images/2016/01/02/210424/14517171